uk.ac.ed.epcc.webapp.forms.inputs

Interface ParseMapInput

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AlternateInput, AlternateItemInput, DataObjectAlternateInput, FileUploadDecorator, ParseMultiInput

    public interface ParseMapInput
    Equivalent of ParseInput for MultiInputs If an Input implements this interface then it wants to directly parse a map of all form inputs because of interactions between the sub-inputs.
    See Also:
    AlternateInput
